":336,"score":-323,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:31:25.000Z","msg":"點解FG人工一定要低過你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T03:46:18.000Z","msg":"講緊香港新移民 腦細係呀爺"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:56:01.000Z","msg":"爺你老母咩2019仲呀爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:30:25.000Z","msg":"成班友認賊作爺<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"64646034778713cb170b11064ee6949d9dc3de44","tid":1191513,"uid":114275,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:34:52.000Z","msg":"無錯 <br />\n<br />\n下星期一我地都會繼續返工 <br />\n<br />\n間公司唔會因為我地聽日出嚟就執笠<br />\n<br />\n但係聽日我同我老婆都會出嚟屌個老細<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無為乜<br />\n<br />\n純粹因為我地應該咁做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你可以一齊嚟 可以唔嚟<br />\n<br />\n但無論你揀乜都好 最後件事一定會影響到你<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到時你記得自己揀過乜野就得"},{"pid":"bc0cd3beba3b3317638702520d919203618efadf","tid":1191513,"uid":126362,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:46:29.000Z","msg":"出來做野咁耐<br />\n班老屎忽永遠都睇唔起有要求既新同事<br />\n佢地覺得你有要求就係搞事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你頂唔順咪走囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但係如果老細壓落嚟搞班老屎忽<br />\n佢哋就大聲啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我真係見唔少呢D老屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n所以根本唔洗理佢地，樓主食花生啦"},{"pid":"e8984760ed5606e6c13fae2624eae87b3945cd97","tid":1191513,"uid":33660,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T05:53:48.000Z","msg":"諗左幾耐？有啲低質"},{"pid":"f6e1b1641a27b853d5501bee2e7cccfd6eb250ca","tid":1191513,"uid":8461,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"a4407406eb54176b323d3093e3