ets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32225b1a57874939bb510dafe4e3f80e52744680","tid":1191513,"uid":29510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:22:16.000Z","msg":"係呀，我都試過<br />\n我地成公司都好撚不滿老世，話要搞革命、要所有人表態<br />\n但係班友對老闆又惡唔出樣，只係全部人不記名咁聯合寫封信俾老闆，話怕俾人炒<br />\n<br />\n我就成為左代罪羔羊，公司有CFO, COO, 各部門經理，都冇表態，但冇人敢搞佢地，因為佢地位高權重<br />\n<br />\n但係就迫我呢個岩岩靠自己努力，做左七年，日日OT起碼兩個鐘既助理經理仔表態，仲要我出埋實名，喺信上面落名做帶頭果個<br />\n<br />\n我到最尾俾人炒撚左，亦俾全行封殺，搵唔到工<br />\n其他迫我表態果班人，因為老闆根本唔知係邊個，當無事發生，繼續返工"},{"pid":"de3346ab3b8c7104d0d86644112b4dfe3f0c3d72","tid":1191513,"uid":119996,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"10ae674dc357d12dd2d756622db151e2bceddc4a","tid":1191513,"uid":58335,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bd7f9b7ae823dab051d9f25fabcbf7574aadc3fc","tid":1191513,"uid":119996,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"518e8ad1974b09cd2b0bcc82319e47e49685191f","tid":1191513,"uid":22574,"like":192,"dislike":0,"score":192,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:01:20.000Z","msg":"都好直，D人點解會睇唔明<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nBTW正評左"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T04:42:37.000Z","msg":"一睇就知有弦外之音<br />\n不過唔好高估00後<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:22:06.000Z","msg":"00後有腦就唔會奶共啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:24:30.000Z","msg":"我哋啲老野識條春咩<br />\n人哋識上深圳潮玩<br />\n我哋上連登廢嗡<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7a3c5101985f111e06f6145d5db42192e7b50dc4","tid":1191513,"uid":119996,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"32225b1a57874939bb510dafe4e3f80e52744680","tid":1191513,"uid":29510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-08T06:22:16.000Z","msg":"係呀，我都試過<br />\n我地成公司都好撚不滿老世，話